column6: "WHOLE PLANET TAKEOVER" Daisy Johnson goes on a hunt to a gun planet. Which is a planet that is an actual gun. Ventolin versus [REDACTED], and the lies fly wide and far. Or do they? The transdimensional team-up: Bucky #1 and Bucky #2 are ready to sort things out.
column8: | writer:Ales Kot | penciller (cover):Michael Del Mundo | artist:Marco Rudy
